aprove.Framework.IntTRS.Nonterm.GeoNonTerm

Class GNAVariableVector

  • java.lang.Object
    • aprove.Framework.IntTRS.Nonterm.GeoNonTerm.GNAVariableVector

  • public class GNAVariableVector
extends java.lang.Object
    This Class defines a vector similar to the GNAVector, with the difference, that this vector can contain variables within the vector. Since this is not possible to store within an int-array thsi class can not be an extension of the GNAVector-class.
    It contains a subset of methods of GNAVector.
    It is used within the GeoNonTermAnalysis to represent vectors containing variables for the SMT-Solver
    Author:
    Timo Bergerbusch
    See Also:
    GeoNonTermAnalysis, SMTFactory

      • getTreeOfVector

        public RPNNode getTreeOfVector()
        this method analyzes the entry's, creates a RPNTree of every entry sometimes using createRecursiveMult(ArrayList) and multiplying integer coefficients and finally uses createRecursiveAdd(ArrayList) to add up all the entry's.
        Returns:
        a RPNNode (a RPNFunctionSymbol) representing the sum of the entry's as a RPNTree
